
# AI Based Smart Classroom Attendance & Analytics System

## Complete To-Do List (Start → Final Deployment)


# 1. Project Planning (First Step)

First, define the clear structure of the project.

### Problem

* Manual attendance is time-consuming.
* Proxy attendance can occur easily.
* Teachers cannot measure classroom engagement.

### Solution

* Face recognition based attendance system
* Engagement detection using computer vision
* Analytics dashboard for attendance insights

### Users

* Admin
* Teacher
* Student

### Modules

* Face Recognition Attendance
* Engagement Detection
* Attendance Database
* Analytics Dashboard
* Automatic Report Generator

---

# 2. Technology Stack Selection

Recommended technology stack for this project:

### Frontend

* HTML
* CSS
* JavaScript

### Backend

* Python
* Flask Framework

### Database

* MySQL or SQLite

### AI / Computer Vision

* OpenCV
* MediaPipe (Face landmarks + tracking)
* Custom Face Matching Logic (instead of face-recognition/dlib)

### Data Visualization

* Chart.js

---

